{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"5":"Prayer (Kitab Al-Salat): Voluntary Prayers"},"section_detail":{"5":{"hadithnumber_first":1250,"hadithnumber_last":1370,"arabicnumber_first":1250,"arabicnumber_last":1370}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1279,"arabicnumber":1279,"text":"Al-Aswad et Masruq ont dit : Nous attestons que ‘Aishah رضي الله عنها a dit : « Il ne se passait pas un jour sans que le Prophète ﷺ ne prie deux rak‘as après la prière du ‘Asr. »","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Bukhari (593) Sahih Muslim (835)"}],"reference":{"book":5,"hadith":30}}]}